      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To authorize the Federal Trade Commission, in consultation with the Federal Communications Commission, to review volume usage service plans of major broadband Internet service providers to ensure that such plans are fairly based on cost.</title>
